Searching records - exact match

1. Open any module to search. Here we opened the Catalog (VP).

We are logged in as Earth Sciences Collections Manager, but we still are able to search across collections.

2. Click the icon next to the "Collection" field
3. Click "Ethnological Art"

Notice that we can see all collections available on the database, even the ones not in Earth Sciences.

4. Click "OK"
5. Surround your terms with \" to perform an exact search

Notice that your selection was added as a text value to the "Collection" field. It is surrounded by the characters \".

\"search terms as many as you would like\"

6. Click the "Search" icon

The results should return all the records in the "Ethnological Art" collection.
